{"tid":453193,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone X 真機 華強北疑似搶先流出？","createTime":"2017-10-31T03:22:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-01T02:39:24.000Z","uid":64181,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e77caa9e01ee89e6aa5a0269d36aea5bd119c5ff","tid":453193,"uid":64181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T03:22:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/1935000/1936248/20171030_iphonex_02_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1935000%2F1936248%2F20171030_iphonex_02_1024.jpg&h=ff554556&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\niPhone X 將於 11 月 3 日本周五，在包括香港等全球多個國家及地區首批開賣。果農果粉等到頸長之際，<a href=\"http://ezone.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fezone.hk&d=alRAh8a4Kj3gHcfQw0fSxmi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=01916a45\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ezone.hk</a> 記者剛收到探子來料，iPhone X 真機竟已搶先在中國流出？<br />\n<br />\n已激活保養期<br />\n<br />\n是咁的，<a href=\"http://ezone.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fezone.hk&d=alRAh8a4Kj3gHcfQw0fSxmi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=01916a45\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ezone.hk</a> 記者收到探子傳來一張截圖（如下），截圖標題為「你的保修服務和支持期限」。從截圖標題及資料顯示，這是一部被激活了的 iPhone X，序列號為 F2LVK116JCLJ；已驗證有效購買日期；免費電話技術支援到期日為 2018 年 1 月 26 日；兼且是一部由中國 Apple 提供保養的中國行貨 iPhone X，已經啟動了保養期，到期日是 2018 年 10 月 27 日。以 iPhone X 享有 1 年保養期計算，咦，莫非是上周五中國 AOS 網上訂購開始時，這部 iPhone X 真機就已經流出市場被激活？是華強北嗎？<br />\n<br />\n中國疑似貨源充足<br />\n<br />\n上周五 iPhone X 的 AOS 網上訂購與 iReserve（ARS）網上預約同步開放，然而很多果農果粉都表示預訂不成功，似乎非常缺貨。那邊廂的中國版 iPhone X 網上訂購卻似是長開長有，貨源充足。<br />\n<br />\n如今更疑似提早流出 iPhone X 中國行貨真機被激活，中國 iPhone X 唔是貨量多到搶先幾天溢出呀嘛？  <br />\n<br />\n一直關心 iPhone X 炒價與 iPhone X 回收價的果農，如果驚，飲杯熱茶，可以定驚的。"},{"pid":"96b70f0c0e722f56e6510a23561fcd16cdccf90e","tid":453193,"uid":64181,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T03:22:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1936248\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F1936248&h=2403339e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2c44473bb5b47d1bfccf9aad75bb5de8b05af6b9","tid":453193,"uid":64181,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T03:23:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1936248\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F1936248&d=alRAh8a4Kj3gHcfQw0fSxmi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=a190a20f\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1936248</a>"},{"pid":"f16f420a6028990bf514a4b6e772f4baeb818903","tid":453193,"uid":64181,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T03:23:25.000Z","msg":"一定係先達狗改圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51785f59d932bbebc613ad0eb4cfd4422426655a","tid":453193,"uid":281,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T03:35:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"565d6782a5299f9fa568ae8146e86603ce6644d2","tid":453193,"uid":23833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T03:55:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要cut埋IR啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好撚慘呀仆街"},{"pid":"1bd6c2bc8ff6c3161a264b9d564b7dc71c500aab","tid":453193,"uid":12575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T05:54:55.000Z","msg":"點樣cut ir架樓豬<br />\n教教我可以嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3ac152bdcf905a57634268374b4f3fa6d489e0d","tid":453193,"uid":64181,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T06:52:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點樣cut ir架樓豬<br />\n教教我可以嗎<img src=\"/asset